Package: treemapify
Title: Draw treemaps easily
Version: 0.1
Author: David Wilkins <david@wilkox.org>
Maintainer: David Wilkins <david@wilkox.org>
Description: Functions to create treemaps with maximum automation and minimum
    effort.
Depends:
    ggplot2,
    plyr (>= 1.3),
    reshape2
License: GPL version 3 or newer.
The G20 dataset is from the Wikipedia article G-20 major economies (http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/G-20_major_economies), which is released under the Creative Commons Attribution-Share-Alike License 3.0.
LazyData: true
